  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK355">
<l>epporu ḷettaṉmait tāyiṉu mapporuḷ</l>
<l>meypporuḷ kāṇpa taṟivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(True) knowledge is the perception concerning every thing of whatever kind, that that thing is the true thing.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
